== 事件 ==

* 9月22日 － [[艾尼克斯|艾尼克斯]]以株式会社营团社募集服务中心名义建立。
* 秋季 － [[米罗华|米罗华]]停产原版[[米罗华奥德赛|奥德赛]]游戏机<ref name="odyssey">{{cite web| author=Winter, David| year=2006| title=Magnavox Odyssey: The first home video game console| url=http://www.pong-story.com/odyssey.htm| work=[http://www.pong-story.com/ pong-story.com]| accessdate=17 February 2006| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060221124902/http://www.pong-story.com/odyssey.htm| archivedate=2006-02-21| deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 知名发行 ==

=== 电子游戏机 ===

* 9月 － [[Epoch|Epoch]]发行日本首款家用游戏机[[TV_Tennis_Electrotennis|TV Tennis Electrotennis]]。主机最独特的是支持[[超高频|UHF]]天线的[[无线|无线]]功能<ref>Martin Picard, [http://gamestudies.org/1302/articles/picard The Foundation of Geemu: A Brief History of Early Japanese video games] {{Wayback|url=http://gamestudies.org/1302/articles/picard |date=20150624050100 }}, ''International Journal of Computer Game Research'', 2013</ref>。
* 12月 － [[雅达利|雅达利]]和Tele-Games（ [[Sears_Holdings_Corporation|Sears, Roebuck and Company]]的一个部门）通过西尔斯百货商店正式发行家用版《[[乓|乓]]》<ref name="pong">{{cite web | author=[[KCTS-TV|KCTS-TV]] | title=History of Gaming / Interactive Timeline of Game History | url=http://www.pbs.org/kcts/videogamerevolution/history/timeline_flash.html | accessdate=17 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060218080821/http://www.pbs.org/kcts/videogamerevolution/history/timeline_flash.html | archivedate=2006-02-18 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。
* 米罗华发行两款新型号奥德赛主机：奥德赛100和奥德赛200<ref name="odyssey" />。

=== 游戏 ===

* 2月 － [[Midway_Games|Midway]]在北美以《Wheels》名义，发行[[西角友宏|西角友宏]]设计的[[Taito|Taito]]1974年街机竞速游戏《[[Speed_Race|Speed Race]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://allincolorforaquarter.blogspot.co.uk/2013/11/video-game-firsts.html |title=The Golden Age Arcade Historian: Video Game Firsts??<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2015-01-23 |archive-date=2017-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105041440/http://allincolorforaquarter.blogspot.co.uk/2013/11/video-game-firsts.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> and ''Racer''.<ref name="Barton">Bill Loguidice & Matt Barton (2009), ''Vintage games: an insider look at the history of Grand Theft Auto, Super Mario, and the most influential games of all time'', p. 197, [[Focal_Press|Focal Press]], ISBN 0-240-81146-1</ref>。
* 2月 － [[诺兰·布什内尔|诺兰·布什内尔]]建立的Horror Games发行了他们唯一的游戏《[[Shark_Jaws|Shark Jaws]]》，意图借助[[斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格|斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格]]电影《[[大白鯊_(電影)|Jaws]]》的知名度赚钱<ref name="icwhen">{{cite web | author=Thomas, Donald A. Jr. | year=2005 | title=–1975– | url=http://www.icwhen.com/book/the_1970s/1975.shtml | accessdate=17 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060312080525/http://www.icwhen.com/book/the_1970s/1975.shtml | archivedate=2006-03-12 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
* Taito发行了最早支持双人[[动作游戏|对战]]的游戏《[[Western_Gun''''''''''|Western Gun'''''''''']]》<ref name="gamespy2">{{cite web|last=Cassidy|first=William|title=Gun Fight|url=http://uk.gamespy.com/articles/491/491634p2.html|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|accessdate=14 September 2012|date=May 6, 2002|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130124064335/http://uk.gamespy.com/articles/491/491634p2.html|archivedate=2013-01-24}}</ref><ref name="Steinberg">{{citation|title=Boy Culture: An Encyclopedia|volume=1|author=Shirley R. Steinberg|editor=Shirley R. Steinberg, Michael Kehler, Lindsay Cornish|publisher=[[ABC-CLIO|ABC-CLIO]]|year=2010|isbn=0-313-35080-9|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=XRGEIqzv5rsC|accessdate=2011-04-02|page=451|archive-date=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012194355/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=XRGEIqzv5rsC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏由西角友宏设计，双玩家各使用两支八向[[控制杆|控制杆]]，一支移动电脑牛仔在画面上移动，另一支改变设计方向<ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web|author=Stephen Totilo|title=In Search Of The First Video Game Gun|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=August 31, 2010|url=http://kotaku.com/5626466/in-search-of-the-first-video-game-gun|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2018-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124133826/https://kotaku.com/5626466/in-search-of-the-first-video-game-gun|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{KLOV game|10420|Western Gun}}</ref>。
* 11月 － Midway发行Taito《Western Gun》的改版《Gun Fight》，是首个基于[[微处理器|微处理器]]的电子游戏<ref name="gunfight">{{cite web | author=Bousiges, Alexis | year=2005 | title=Gun Fight | url=http://www.arcade-history.com/index.php?page=detail&id=1040 | accessdate=17 February 2006 | archive-date=2020-11-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127213519/https://www.arcade-history.com/index.php?page=detail&id=1040 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。Taito的《Western Gun》使用[[晶体管－晶体管逻辑|TTL构架]]硬件，而美版由[[Dave_Nutting_Associates|Dave Nutting Associates]]移植到[[Intel_8080|Intel 8080]]微处理器<ref name="gunfight2">{{cite web | title=Western Gun | url=http://emustatus.rainemu.com/games/westerngun.htm | work=Emulation Status | accessdate=19 February 2006 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123095723/http://emustatus.rainemu.com/games/westerngun.htm | archive-date=2015-01-23 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
* [[Don_Daglow|Don Daglow]]在[[PDP-10|PDP-10]]上开发早期[[电子角色扮演游戏|电子角色扮演游戏]]《[[Dungeon_(游戏)|Dungeon]]》<ref name="dungeon">{{cite web | author=Maragos, Nich | year=2004 | title=Talking: Don Daglow | url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3133666&did=1 | accessdate=17 February 2006 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041013061213/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3133666&did=1 | archivedate=2004年10月13日 }}</ref>。
* [[威廉·克劳瑟|威廉·克劳瑟]]在PDP-10上开发第一款[[视觉小说|视觉小说]]游戏《[[Colossal_Cave_Adventure|Adventure]]》（又名“Colossal Cave”和“Advent”）<ref name="adventure">{{cite web | author=Adams, Rick | title=A history of 'Adventure' | url=http://www.rickadams.org/adventure/a_history.html | accessdate=17 February 2006 | archive-date=2011-05-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517000635/http://www.rickadams.org/adventure/a_history.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* Rusty Rutherford 在[[柏拉图系统|柏拉图系统]]上开发最早的[[迷宫探索|迷宫探索]]游戏《[[pedit5|pedit5]]》<ref name="pedit5">{{cite web| author=Rusty Rutherford| title=The Creation of PEDIT5| url=http://armchairarcade.com/neo/node/1948| accessdate=10 June 2011| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707162725/http://armchairarcade.com/neo/node/1948| archivedate=2011-07-07| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。
* 《[[Dnd_(电子游戏)|dnd]]》——首款有[[头目_(角色类型)|头目]]的电子游戏，可说是最早的[[电子角色扮演游戏|电子角色扮演游戏]]——结束了最初开发。部分来源将游戏归入1974年；但不清楚游戏那时是否可玩。

